  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/0b8d7aedd93a699c75182d6d031b536e.avif?t=1733006867\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤠 Roguelike of duels in the Wild West.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 Challenge the fiercest gunslingers in intense card duels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏 Collect and build your deck with unique ability and weapon cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏜️ Explore a map full of dangers and opportunities different in each game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️ Unlock cards, enemies, characters, and increasingly difficult challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤖 Face bosses with special abilities and unique strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 Tactical decisions that will change the course of each duel.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📜 Discover the hidden history of the Wild West through your adventures.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/6f775474ea3952302dd9c572ef240a28.avif?t=1733006867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras_big/6f775474ea3952302dd9c572ef240a28.avif?t=1733006867 width=800 height=167 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/272f3d26b04202bc111fbc07b01bbf6d.poster.avif?t=1733006867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/272f3d26b04202bc111fbc07b01bbf6d.webm?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/272f3d26b04202bc111fbc07b01bbf6d.mp4?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active Cards: These cards are the ones you'll directly use in duels. They can include attacks, defenses, special moves, and more. Using them wisely is key to defeating your opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Passive Cards: These cards add special abilities and bonuses to your character. They can improve your stats, grant new passive abilities, or even modify the game rules in your favor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain your cards by winning duels, purchasing them from the shop, or discovering loot scenes scattered throughout the map for unexpected rewards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/02db5aae79784b759a479bac13698e76.avif?t=1733006867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras_big/02db5aae79784b759a479bac13698e76.avif?t=1733006867 width=800 height=167 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/cab34c65f3ce4e72825a225a956ac2f0.poster.avif?t=1733006867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/cab34c65f3ce4e72825a225a956ac2f0.webm?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/cab34c65f3ce4e72825a225a956ac2f0.mp4?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every duel immerses you in a unique encounter against random enemies, providing a dynamic and thrilling gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to challenge bosses of incredible strength and cunning, who lead formidable and strategically crafted decks of cards. These battles will test your tactical skill and prowess in every move.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Showcase your bravery and skill! Only the most cunning, daring, and well-prepared duelists can overcome the challenges of Duelite's Wild West.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/5c9a092ed97ceb410193d8f2a8bbf570.avif?t=1733006867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras_big/5c9a092ed97ceb410193d8f2a8bbf570.avif?t=1733006867 width=800 height=167 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/1c954d2375a322054a751d872aa90ace.poster.avif?t=1733006867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/1c954d2375a322054a751d872aa90ace.webm?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/1c954d2375a322054a751d872aa90ace.mp4?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select your character and play with an initial deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a new world in each game with unique maps, enemies, cards, and scenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your active and passive cards according to each game's needs, where strategy and decision-making are crucial to capturing the most wanted.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/2cf273106e147bb0824ade2f76203e07.avif?t=1733006867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras_big/2cf273106e147bb0824ade2f76203e07.avif?t=1733006867 width=800 height=167 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/b7f967b07f13d003b107b9938e9d8ce5.poster.avif?t=1733006867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/b7f967b07f13d003b107b9938e9d8ce5.webm?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961480/extras/b7f967b07f13d003b107b9938e9d8ce5.mp4?t=1733006867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover collection albums that you can complete to unlock special rewards and expand your gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you play an active or passive card, it will be added to its corresponding album as a collectible. Collectors can complete these albums while progressing through the game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, we also have an album for enemies and bosses. Defeat them all and complete it!</p></li></ul>",
